quote.summary: Wuxi Lead Intelligent Equipment Co Ltd is a China-based company primarily engaged in the research, design, production, and sales of intelligent equipment, as well as the provision of solutions. The Company's main products include lithium-ion battery intelligent equipment, photovoltaic(PV) intelligent equipment, computer, communication and consumer electronics (3C) intelligent equipment, and intelligent logistics equipment. The Company is also engaged in the provision of other intelligent equipment and solutions, including hydrogen energy intelligent equipment, automotive intelligent production line, and laser precision processing equipment. The Company distributes its products within the domestic market and to overseas markets such as Europe and North America.
